lead_paragraph: Olympique Lyonnais moved into provisional second place in Ligue 1 with a deserved 2-0 win at Montpellier thanks to two first-half goals from winger Maxwell Cornet on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Cornet on Song With Double as Lyon Move Up to Second
headline.main: Cornet on Song With Double as Lyon Move Up to Second
